Wx-TreeListCtrl
===============


A simple wrapper around the wxWidgets class wxTreeListCtrl.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires wxWidgets and wxPerl:

